 (Highest Quality)'=>'Gemini 2.5 Pro — Stabil (Højeste kvalitet)','GPT-5.4 Mini ⚡ (Fast & Smart)'=>'GPT-5.4 Mini ⚡ (Hurtig og smart)','GPT-5.4 Frontier (Flagship Intelligence)'=>'GPT-5.4 Frontier (Flagskibs-intelligens)','GPT-4o (Legacy Stable)'=>'GPT-4o (Gammel stabil)','GPT-4o Mini (Legacy Budget)'=>'GPT-4o Mini (Gammel budget)','Claude Sonnet 4.6 (Most Balanced)'=>'Claude Sonnet 4.6 (Mest balanceret)','Claude Opus 4.6 (Supreme Reasoning)'=>'Claude Opus 4.6 (Højeste ræsonnement)','Claude 3.5 Sonnet (Legacy)'=>'Claude 3.5 Sonnet (Gammel)','Reasoning Intensity'=>'Ræsonnement-intensitet','Auto (Balanced)'=>'Auto (Balanceret)','Low (Speed Focused)'=>'Lav (Hastighedsfokuseret)','Medium (Deeper Reasoning)'=>'Medium (Dybere ræsonnement)','High (Advanced Complex)'=>'Høj (Avanceret kompleks)','Higher intensity increases intelligence and accuracy but raises operational token costs. (GPT-5.4 & Claude 4.6+)'=>'Højere intensitet øger intelligens, men også omkostninger. (GPT-5.4 & Claude 4.6+)','Fallback models are used when the primary connection is overloaded. Note: Fallback models may have different pricing profiles than your primary selection.'=>'Reservemodeller bruges ved overbelastning. Bemærk: Priser kan variere.','The chat sessions table could not be created. Please deactivate and reactivate the plugin, or contact support.'=>'Chattabellen kunne ikke oprettes. Prøv at genaktivere plugin.','Modern Hotel Booking:'=>'Moderne hotelbooking:','Fix in Settings → General'=>'Ret i Indstillinger → Generelt','Saving…'=>'Gemmer…','Deleting…'=>'Sletter…','Error — try again'=>'Fejl — prøv igen','(Compulsory — auto-applied)'=>'(Obligatorisk — automatisk anvendt)','Compulsory Fee'=>'Obligatorisk gebyr','Automatically add to every booking (not selectable by guest)'=>'Tilføj automatisk til hver booking (kan ikke fravælges af gæsten)','Use for cleaning fees, resort fees, or any mandatory service charge. The fee will appear as a locked line item on the booking form and in emails.'=>'Brug ti